E1A2AUD.original: ~z~If I close my eyes they can't see me, if I close my eyes they can't see me.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~闭上眼睛他们就看不见我，闭上眼睛他们就看不见我。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Uhh, aight. I'm up on Y in Northwood. See you in a minute.
~z~A quick kidnapping's a good kidnapping. Come on.
~z~Lord, I am sorry for shitting myself.
~z~How the fuck we meant to snatch a man-up when we ain't got nothing to put him in?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~装人的车都没了，这他妈绑架个屁啊？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We need four wheels, I got that.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~必须得开四个轮子，我准备了一辆。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Much as I like rolling with an escort, we really got to lose these fucking oinkers.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~虽然我很喜欢遛条子，但这次真得甩了他们。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Listen, buddy. Ashley is square with you now.
~z~Is that a fact? I'll bare that in mind, Malc.
~z~I know I am, Johnny. And you know what's the best thing about me? You. Call me, okay?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我也知道，Johnny。你知道我最大的幸运是什么吗？是你。多联系，好吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Lord, I am sorry for all the women I've chased,
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~主啊，我不该对女人三心二意，

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I think I'm having a heart attack. I feel numb. Oh God, oh God.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~好像要犯心脏病了，我有点麻了。噢天哪，噢天哪。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Damn, Johnny. I thought you cared about me. You can't leave me like this. Johnny...
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Johnny。我还以为你在乎我。你怎么能这样对我，Johnny...

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I don't know, I ain't hearing shit.
~z~Sure, sure she ain't. Thats why you running all over town trying to snatch a fool up, huh? Please.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~对，当然不是。所以才要大老远地去绑架一个傻逼？别吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You have got yourselves the best Limo driver in the whole of Liberty City.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你们有幸遇到了自由城最好的豪车司机。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We got two college coeds over here and,
~z~Don't try nothing, chubby. It ain't like you're a difficult target to hit.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~别耍小聪明，肥仔。要打中你小菜一碟。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~So do me a favor, go easy on the fat man.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~就当给我个面子，别对这胖子太狠。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I'll fucking kill you if you run again, fatty.
~z~Shit's hot, Johnny. Get these motherfuckers off us.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~出岔子了，Johnny。快把傻逼条子甩了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We doing this for your girl, so you do the running.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~为了你的娘们才来的，你去追他。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Head for the hills, Roman. Come on!
~z~We ain't kidnapping nobody because of my mamma, Johnny. It's your lady friend getting us to do this. Think on that, son.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们不是因为我妈才来绑架别人的，Johnny。~n~都是因为你的女性朋友。动动脑子，小子。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~How did a fat motherfucker like that get away from two young fit dudes like us?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~死胖子怎么会从我们两个年轻壮汉手里逃掉的？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah you're right man, we ain't snatching that guy today.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~确实是这样，老兄，今天没法绑架他了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Ahhhh. Help me. Someone. I'm too young to die. Please.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~啊啊啊，救命啊！来人啊！我还不想死啊！拜托！

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I think he's trying to say something, Malc.
~z~Okay, now all we got to do is wait for this guy to come out of there.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~好了，现在只需要等他自投罗网了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~in debt to some Russians. You down? I'll pay.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~还欠俄罗斯人钱。你来吗？我出钱。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I knew you were a fucking racist. I fucking knew it. Stop the car.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~就知道你是个种族主义者，我就知道。给我停车。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You should apologize for that smell. You shat yourself or something?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你还是先为自己的臭味道歉吧。你是拉裤子了吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Did you mean to insult us, Mr. Roman Bellic? I sure hope not.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你是存心侮辱我们吗，Roman Bellic？希望不是。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We gotta take the fat man to a warehouse in Bohan.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们要把这个胖子送到Bohan的一间仓库。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Fucking you up the ass with a barb wire dick would be a pleasure for this man.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~他很乐意用染着淋病的大鸡巴对你狂暴轰入。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, that's what I said. Maybe Italian or Rome or some shit.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~对，就是这个意思。~n~也可能是意大利或者罗马那边的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I got a leash on him now, don't worry 'bout a thing.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~现在我把他拴上了，不用担心。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You pull a stunt like that again, and it's over for you, bacon ass.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~再敢耍这种花招，你就死定了，大屁股。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Alright man, but I'm driving the cage.
~z~Most Europeans are gay, man. That's why they wear them tight-ass jeans.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~欧洲基佬多，兄弟。所以他们都穿紧身牛仔裤。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Aight just this year, man, we ain't got time for all that shit.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~单算今年吧，兄弟，没空翻那些旧账了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Hey there, babe. Something went wrong. This job isn't happening. Stay safe.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你好啊，宝贝。出了点岔子。绑架失败了。注意安全。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I'll take you through the bright lights of Star Junction, past the glamorous shops of Middle Park West,
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我会带你们穿越星汇广场的灯火辉煌，看遍中心公园西的繁荣市场。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I'm hoping he ain't too good at poker. Hell, if we're here because of his debts, he can't exactly be the Buffet Car.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~希望他牌技没那么好。妈的，他都欠债到要被人绑架了，总不能是赌神吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Shut the fuck up, you fat prick.
~z~Do that again and you're a dead man. A fat dead man.
~z~I think he's on a hot date or something. What is it you need from him?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~现在他可能正在约会。您有什么事要找他吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Hit the road, fat man. I'm not in the kidnapping mood right now.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~滚蛋吧，胖子。我现在没心情绑架你。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Can't you see I'm trying to drive here? You fucking pop him.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~没看见老子在开车吗？要崩你崩。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~What is all this fuss about his cousin?
~z~So, we got a plan, Johnny boy?
~z~You're here. You're here. Oh man... Johnny...
~z~Who is this guy? Why you want him snatched?
~z~Oh, Johnny. I fucked up. I fucked up real bad.
~z~I hope this motherfucker hurries up and loses his money so we can snatch him.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~希望这个傻逼赶紧把钱输完，出来让我们抓。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah this has got to be kind of awkward, man. I'm going to slip off. Peace.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，这次是不太对，老兄。我先溜了。再见。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah this has got to be kind of awkward, man. I'm going to slip off. Peace.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，这次是不太对，老兄。我先溜了。再见。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Oh Lord, I apologise for sleeping with those twins.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~噢，主啊，我不该睡那对双胞胎的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Sooner you get over there the sooner this will all be over with.
~z~Well, uh, that kidnapping - didn't go too well, did it?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~好吧...绑架的事，好像不太顺利啊。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Hey now listen, I do mean motherfucker in the most literal sense. Serious incest motherfucker.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你听好了，这个「日妈」可是~n~字面意思的日妈。日了自己的亲妈。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Ummm.... ahhhh... I... Mr. Bellic is very busy man. An important and busy man.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~呃...啊...我...Bellic先生是个大忙人。~n~是一位重要的大忙人。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~He ain't gonna make a play like that again. Believe that.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~他没机会再跑一次了。相信我。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~The Lost aren't like those Deadbeats. Take a look at my brothers, man.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~失落帮可跟死妈天使不一样。~n~瞧瞧我那些弟兄，伙计。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~If he only knew how close he came though. Thanks, Malc.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~可惜他不知道自己离危险有多近。谢了，Malc。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~How do you like Bohan, Mr. Bellic? Some pals are waiting for you there.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你喜欢Bohan吗，Bellic先生？有人在那里等你。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~From the smell, it ain't just piss. I'm glad I ain't sitting back there with him.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~闻起来不止是尿了。还好我不用坐在后排。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I've seen some of those bodies you people dump in the Humboldt.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我在Humboldt河里看见过你们扔掉的尸体。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Oh shit, Johnny. Shit. What happened? I thought you were looking out for me.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~噢，天哪，Johnny。妈的，什么情况？你不是会帮我的吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Hell no, I don't wanna get my hands all dirty and shit. Get gravy all on my new manicured fingers.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~不干，我才不想脏了自己的手。刚修过指甲不想沾油。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, shut the fuck up. Ya heard?
~z~Hello, this is Bellic and Bellic Enterprises. What can I assist you with?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~您好，这里是 Bellic&Bellic 集团。有什么我能帮您的吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, man. I'll make sure it don't repeat itself.
~z~Get in the car, fat man. Your ass has just been snatched.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~回到车上，胖子。你小子被绑架了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We let him go and he'll come back with a bag full of unmarked twenties, right?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们把他放走，以后他就会给我们一麻袋没被标记的20块，对吧？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Alright, you win. I know when to fold my hand.
~z~It's easy. You grab him and deliver him to warehouse, off Lompoc in Bohan Industrial.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~很简单。绑架他，然后送到Bohan工业区Lompoc大道那里的仓库。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~So, yeah this guy we're snatching isn't the only European-type dude I've come across recently.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~其实，在这次绑架之前我已经遇到过一个欧洲人了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You know, Malc, I think you've got unresolved women issues.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~知道吗，Malc，我觉得你有没解决的女性情结。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~-No! Wait.~n~-Get in there and shut up!
~z~We'll try to contact Mr. Bellic and have him come as soon as possible.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们会联系Bellic先生，让他尽快过来接送的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Come on, piggly-wiggly. We need some grease or something?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~快点，小猪猪。给我们来点脂肪。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I don't know. Both maybe. Fuck it. Shut up for a second.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我不知道，都有可能吧。无所谓了。闭上你的嘴吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I dunno. I'm doin' this as a favor for a friend.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~不知道，我只是在替朋友帮忙。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I hope he knows that you and me are men of integrity, Malc.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~希望他知道我俩都是有原则的人，Malc。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Ashley you gotta stop fucking things up...
~z~If it was a box of donuts you'd get your fat ass in there.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~要是有一盒甜甜圈，你肯定会自己进来。快点，胖子。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, this biker dude is twisted as all hell, man. By the way how many guys you killed, son?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~没错，这位飞车党可是坏得一批，伙计。~n~问一下，你杀了多少人了，小子？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We snatch this guy, deliver him to some other guys, then we pat ourselves on the back for doing a great job.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~先抓住他，再把他送过去，然后互相拍拍后背大功告成。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Shit. I know about brothers, but I know about bitches as well.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我不但了解兄弟，还了解臭娘们呢。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You go get him, he ain't gonna be hard to catch.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你去抓住他，很容易就能抓住他。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Bitch please... your patriotism is making you ignorant.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你妈妈的...无脑爱国会让你坐井观天的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I can't get robbed twice in one day.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~总不能让我一天被抢两次吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Thank God I'm hanging out with another two-bit street philosopher.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我怎么又遇上了个二流街头哲学家。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Were you close to your mother growing up? Did she let you down?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~小时候有妈疼吗？她让你失望了吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Sounds like it's Eastern European or some shit.
~z~You either do it, or junky gets killed.
~z~We're not robbing you, we're taking you.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们不是要抢劫你，是来绑架你的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I nearly had you, buddy. You got to admit that?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我差点就跑掉了，伙计。这你得承认吧？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I told you, I like this gun. I ain't getting no bodies on it. Not today.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~哟，我说了，我喜欢这枪。暂时不想沾上血，现在不行。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Easy, Johnny... you saw the shit stains in the back seat.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~够了，Johnny...后排的屎印你也看见了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Dude, you busy? I got something and I don't need it getting round the clubhouse. I'll owe you, brother.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~老兄，有空吗？我有点事，不能让帮里的兄弟知道。算我欠你的，兄弟。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Told me I was gonna meet some 1950s lookin' motherfucker
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~签语是我会遇到个活在50年代的臭傻逼，

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~-The name of the man we want is Roman Bellic.~n~-Yeah.
~z~Shit, Jay. Can you pop this motherfucker and shut him up?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，J。你能崩他一枪让他闭嘴吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~All the immigrants you meet seem to be from Russia.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~现在能遇到的移民好像都是俄国人。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~the money I have wasted, the internet porn.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~不该浪费钞票，不该上网看片。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~As a matter of fact it did.
~z~That's got to be him. Come on.
~z~-Your woman here owes Dimitri Rascalov a lot of money.~n~-Okay.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~－你的女人欠了Dimitri Rascalov一笔巨款。~n~－好。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yo, lighten up, Johnny boy. I'm just fucking with you son.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~哟，放轻松，Johnny仔。我逗你小子玩呢。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Shit dude, we got to get five-o off our ass.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，老兄，我们被条子盯上了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~What happens to this shithead is none of your concern.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~这个白痴的下场不需要你们关心。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Well, in that case I'll... I mean, ah...
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~行啊，这样的话我马上...我是说，呃...

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Not difficult decision, even for a man stuck in 1960s time warp.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~不难选吧，还活在60年代的你都能选对。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Worked with this other guy, he could handle himself. Maybe this guy will be the same.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~之前跟我合作的人，他就很能打。~n~这家伙估计也有两下子。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Okay, I couldn't run any further if I wanted to.
~z~they're in need of a Limo'. And I'm told this Bellic guy's the man for that kind of work.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~她们需要一辆豪华轿车。~n~别人跟我说这种事得找这位Bellic。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Where you off to, Johnny boy? We kind of in the middle of something right here, man.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你要去哪儿，Johnny仔？我们还有事要办呢，哥们。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You mean, he's like trying to bribe us?
~z~Wait, where are the ladies? Who are you?
~z~It's been a good year, you know?
~z~I messed up, baby... promise you won't be mad.
~z~-My name is not important.~n~-What is this?
~z~Okay. Okay. My cousin, he has money. He will pay you.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~好的，好的。我堂弟，他有钱。他会给你们钱。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Man, I just got me this nine. I don't wanna go puttin' no bodies on it already.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我这枪新换的，不想这么快就沾上血。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Nah. A living hostage is one of the prerequisites for a successful snatching, ain't it?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~确实。人质活着才能算成功的绑架吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~If you want Wingit Presentation before every job you do, you're running with the wrong crowd.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~做什么事之前都要长篇大论，我又不是那种领导。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~And this here job - smells like a bitch to me. It got bitch-stink all over it, son.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~这次的活儿，闻着就像是臭娘们。一股子骚味儿，小子。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~What do you want the shirt off my back? Come on.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你们想要啥？我的底裤吗？拜托。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Or in your case, guys coming from a 1950s time warp.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你不也一样，现在还活在50年代。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~She's a friend and she's in trouble. I believe in looking out for people you've been close to.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~她是我的朋友，现在陷入了麻烦。~n~我向来都会照顾身边的人的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~but hangs around some backroom gambling place on Dillon Street in Schottler.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~但他经常去一家地下赌场，在Schottler的Dillon街。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Well, I'm not in the kidnapping business, dude.
~z~Just pop the fucker. And you can get the bullets outta him afterwards and no one's gonna trace that shit back to you.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~赶紧崩了他。待会儿把子弹掏出来就行了，条子查不到你身上的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah we just stole this guy, too. But I guess we gotta let him go. I'll be seeing the both of you.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~这哥们也是刚绑来的。不过只能放过他了。两位以后再见。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Why are all you bikers racist, just like the Angels of Death?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~就说死亡天使吧，你们飞车党怎么都搞种族歧视？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, man, this job was your idea. What are you doing?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，老兄，找我一起办事，你倒是跑了？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You know, this ain't the first grungy European I've met recently.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~其实最近我刚遇到过一个脏兮兮的欧洲人。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Ashley, you need to tell your Russian loan shark that the guy they're after is dead.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~Ashley，麻烦你转告你的俄国债主，他们要的人死了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Those Russians have got their guy. You got lucky, but you got to control yourself, Ashley.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~人质交给俄国人了。算你走运，麻烦你管住自己，Ashley。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We're lucky that the fat man can't run. Next time, lock the damn hostage up.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~幸好胖子跑不了多远。下次，把人质锁好了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Ummm, Johnny, my dude, we're going to do this or what? What the fuck is wrong with you?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~呃...Johnny，好兄弟，我们还办不办事了？你他妈犯病了是吧？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~who preferred rusty oil dripping junk to hi-tech precision machinery.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~比起高科技精密机械，他更喜欢生锈漏油的破铜烂铁。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~And I'm not in the dude business, dude.
~z~I need to snatch some guy name of uhh, Roman Bellic. Runs a cab firm,
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我要绑架一个叫Roman Bellic的人。开出租车行的，

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We're more like equal opportunity haters - we hate assholes and fools, wherever they're from.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我们倒不如说是一视同仁。~n~不问出身，都他妈傻逼。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Oh, I get it. I think the man's trying to give us some money.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~噢，我懂了。他好像想给我们钱。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~How come all the Slavs in this city wear shitty tracksuits, man?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~怎么这里的斯拉夫人都喜欢穿运动服啊？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~you might end the tour with a look at the finest specimen of manhood in the entire metropolitan area.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你们还可以在旅途结束前见识到~n~整个大都会最有男子气概的人。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Please, gentlemen. The men in there just took my money.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，二位。里面的人刚把我洗劫一空。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~What happened to the days when it was guys coming across from Mexico?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~以前那些偷渡进来的墨西哥人呢？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~-We need you to do us favor.~n~-What?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~－现在需要你帮我们一个忙。~n~－什么忙？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Damn you better not be right. What's wrong with you, man? We was only joshing you. Tell him, Johnny.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，希望你说错了。你他妈有病吧，哥们？~n~我们是开玩笑的。告诉他，Johnny。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Oh, it's like that, is it, now? She like your girlfriend or something? Nah, nah, that's cool. I'm feeling that.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~噢，我差不多能猜到了。就是你的女友之类的吧？这又没关系的。可以理解。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Bellic, I wanted to kidnap you, now I might kill ya.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~Bellic，本来我只是绑架你，现在我都想杀你了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~And not this Rusty Brown's munching, quadruple Bleeder Burger eating motherfucker.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~这个啃着甜甜圈和四层吸血鬼堡的傻逼不行。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Move them fat little legs of yours.
~z~Things is coming together, starting to make sense now.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~这样就对了嘛，我完全明白了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~I'll buy you a new one. Just shut this dude up.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~我给你买新的，你先让他闭嘴。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~If you were meant to be going in the ground, you wouldn't be conversing with us gentlemen like this.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~要是存心想杀你，你哪有机会跟我们聊天啊。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~We need you to kidnap someone for us.
~z~You mean, like, this year or in my whole career?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你是说...单算今年，还是入行以来？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~You and your boys might ride, but you don't know nothing about brotherhood.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你们帮的人确实在骑车，但根本就不了解什么是兄弟情谊。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Somebody looking for a fat Slav with a bladder problem?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~有人在找小便失禁的斯拉夫胖子吗？

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Oh, wait. You hate me because where I'm from? Man, that's cold.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~啥玩意？你居然因为我的出身鄙视我？天，真恶心。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~For future reference, Malc, it might be worth locking your hostages into a car.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~留供日后参考，Malc，绑架别人的时候最好锁住车门。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Well, uh, that kidnapping - didn't go too well, did it?
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~好吧...绑架的事，好像不太顺利啊。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Malc, tell this gentlemen what my kind of people do to guys who try to buy their way out.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~Malc，告诉这位先生，我会怎么对待想花钱走后门的人。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~All you Europeans got the same fucking accent.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~你们欧洲人都他妈一个口音是吧。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~They'll turn me out. I don't know what I'm going to do. Shit.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~他们会杀了我的。我不知道该怎么办了。妈的。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Dammit, dude done pissed his self. That shit ain't right.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，这小子吓尿了。太他妈恶心了。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~The ice got you into this mess.
~z~And that we'd find something like that real insulting.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~贿赂简直就是对我们的侮辱。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Come on. Get back in the car.
~z~You ain't a difficult target to hit, Mr. Bellic.
~z~Huh, huh. Must be a good friend.
~z~Roman Bellic. What the fuck kind of name is that?

E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~求求你，求求你们。我什么都给你。

E1A2AUD.original: ~z~Just so you know who you dealing with, Mr. Bellic. This is one screwed up dumb redneck motherfucker.
E1A2AUD.translated: ~z~先告诉你你面前的人是谁，Bellic先生。~n~这可是一位不好惹的日妈红脖子。
